{"article_id":"qhmTcEIBeguKd4Ns","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"White House Exerts Executive Privilege Over 'Fast And Furious ' Documents","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"The battle between the Obama administration and the House Oversight and Government over the Fast and Furious operation just ratcheted up another notch .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"There 's word","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"that the White House is exerting executive privilege over documents","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"that the committee 's Republican majority has subpoenaed .","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"From The University of Chicago Law School 's Faculty Blog :","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"A primer on executive privilege .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"That news , from NPR 's Carrie Johnson and others on the story , broke just minutes before a committee hearing","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"at which lawmakers are expected to vote on whether to hold Attorney General Eric Holder in contempt of Congress","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"for failing to turn over those documents .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"That hearing is to be webcast here .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"Reuters is reporting","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"that a committee aide says","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"the panel will go forward with the majority plan","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"to cite Holder for contempt .","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"`` Fast and Furious broke into public view after the December 2010 death of a U.S. Border Patrol agent .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"Two guns","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"connected to the botched gun-trafficking operation","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"were found near the body of Brian Terry ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"igniting two congressional probes and an ongoing investigation by the Justice Department 's inspector general . ''","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Holder appeared before the panel on June 7","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"where he faced a grilling from Chairman Darrel Issa , R-Calif. and other Republican lawmakers .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Issa asked Holder","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"if his department knew of the tactics","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"used in the flawed gunrunning operation ,","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"and Republicans accused him of not coming clean","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"and not complying with subpoenas .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"Update at 3:25 p.m . ET :","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"The committee is now going through some proposed amendments to the contempt citation .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Update at 2:20 p.m . ET :","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Obviously , there has n't been a vote before 2 p.m . ET .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"We 'll keep an eye out","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"and report back","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"when it happens .","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"Update at 1:25 p.m . ET .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Vote Before 2 p.m . ET ?","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Issa just announced a recess ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"and said","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"the committee will reconvene 10 minutes after the last House vote of the day ,","depth":14},{"id":39,"text":"which","depth":16},{"id":40,"text":"he said","depth":16},{"id":41,"text":"would come at 1:30 p.m . ET .","depth":15},{"id":42,"text":"So , that would imply a committee vote on the contempt citation sometime after 1:40 p.m . ET .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"The committee has not yet voted on the contempt citation .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Members are still arguing along partisan lines , for","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"( Republicans )","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"and against","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"( Democrats )","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"citing Holder for contempt .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"The Associated Press writes","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"if the committee does vote to hold Holder in contempt ,","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"`` the contempt citation would then go to the full House .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"Eventually , there could be a federal case against Holder ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"but past examples suggest","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"the matter wo n't get that far . ''","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"The lawmakers are still talking .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"They have not yet voted .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"Committee members are still giving their opening statements .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"So far they 've been along part lines","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"- Republicans saying","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"that the Obama administration has been resisting efforts","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"to get information about Fast and Furious ;","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Democrats saying","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"the administration has more than fully cooperated .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"At the start of the hearing , Issa said","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"the committee did not set out to hold Holder in contempt ,","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"but rather to `` get the information","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"the committee needs","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"to complete its work . ''","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"Of the exertion of executive privilege , he said","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"it was `` not spoken of last night ''","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"when committee staffers and Justice Department officials were negotiating .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"He called it `` an untimely assertion by the Justice Department . ''","depth":5},{"id":74,"text":"Carrie forwarded us the two letters","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"written by Justice","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"about the assertion of executive privilege .","depth":4},{"id":77,"text":"Click on the titles","depth":4},{"id":78,"text":"to pop up larger versions :","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":157,"left":0,"right":156,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":156,"left":151,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{